title: 10 Takeaways From Week 7 & Why Sean Payton should be Coach of the Year
itunes:title: 10 Takeaways From Week 7 & Why Sean Payton should be Coach of the Year
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Rhett Lewis open the show to discuss their top takeaways from Week 7, including Aaron Rodgers’ dominant performance against the Raiders (1:05), the Vikings potentially being the most complete team in the league (6:40), the Bills’ formula for their success (9:55), why Sean Payton deserves to be Coach of the Year (21:12), 49ers defense continues to flex (29:15) & the Colts are now the team to beat in the AFC South (33:30).
